                        <interp inst="t18440408-name-242" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS HARDING</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a cashier in the banking house of Sir John William Lubbock and Co. I paid this check all in gold, as far at I know—the sum was £652 0<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—there might have been a mixture of sovereigns and half-sovereigns—it was weighed.</p>
